Ligatures{{Expand section}}

The use of ligature in Arabic is common.  There is one compulsory ligature, that for {{transl}} + {{transl}}, which exists in two forms. All other ligatures ({{transl}} + {{transl}}, etc.) are optional.

Contextual forms Name 
Final Medial Initial Isolated 
